18:17.737 --> 18:21.170
What you did,
that hurt, girl.

18:23.737 --> 18:26.070
Overton, I'm so sorry.

18:26.137 --> 18:28.304
Maybe my lips
were touching his

18:28.370 --> 18:31.970
