18:37.070 --> 18:38.704
I mean, I wanna beleive that.

18:38.770 --> 18:41.504
But things were really
right between us

18:41.570 --> 18:43.504
this never would
have happened.

18:43.570 --> 18:44.770
[sighs]

18:44.837 --> 18:47.737
If there is something wrong,
I say we sit here

18:47.804 --> 18:49.404
review our relationship

18:49.470 --> 18:52.704
and try to figure where
the problem got started.

18:52.770 --> 18:54.637
Okay.

18:54.704 --> 18:56.970
Eighteen months ago

18:57.037 --> 18:59.337
I saw a moving van roll up

18:59.404 --> 19:01.344
saw you in the front seat

19:01.410 --> 19:03.344
and said, "That must be
Khadijah's cousin.

19:03.410 --> 19:06.210
