you get up there

19:37.144 --> 19:39.710
call us and let us know
everything is cool.

19:39.777 --> 19:42.410
Yes, signal us.
Jump off the roof.

19:42.477 --> 19:45.677
And when you pass the window
flash the okay sign.

19:59.410 --> 20:01.350
Yeah, Khadijah.
Yeah, it's me.

20:01.417 --> 20:03.817
No, no, they're fine.
Everything is cool.

20:03.884 --> 20:07.484
No, you can't talk
to her right now.

20:07.550 --> 20:09.284
Trust me, trust me.

20:09.350 --> 20:11.450
She's busy.

20:24.184 --> 20:25.450
You know, Obie

20:25.517 --> 20:29.384
