amazing than I ever dreamed.

20:29.450 --> 20:31.484
And I dream in color.

20:33.417 --> 20:35.717
Yeah, just wish it
wasn't over so fast.

20:40.250 --> 20:43.017
Yeah, I'm sorry
I finished first.

20:46.050 --> 20:49.050
I know that we didnt think
that we were ready to go

20:49.117 --> 20:51.117
