about that time.

20:59.358 --> 21:02.931
I never realized how much
passion I'd saved up for you.

21:02.998 --> 21:05.764
Well, my Lothario old Uncle
Timmy used to say

21:05.831 --> 21:07.798
"Passion is like money.

21:07.864 --> 21:12.231
Time to save it up
and a time to spend it all."

21:13.931 --> 21:17.531
So, what you wanna do now?

21:19.298 --> 21:22.497
Um, take off the hat, daddy.

21:22.563 --> 21:24.497
