21:36.563 --> 21:38.630
You finally got
that damn coat back?

21:38.697 --> 21:40.663
What'd you say
to Max to get it?

21:40.730 --> 21:42.863
I said his $400.

21:45.663 --> 21:48.697
Hey, Regine, that money you
gave me for that crummy coat

21:48.763 --> 21:50.097
