21:58.663 --> 22:00.603
Same box I got that coat.

22:00.670 --> 22:03.103
Oh, I took a whole
lotta stuff.

22:04.837 --> 22:08.037
That's my sweater
and I want it back.

22:08.103 --> 22:10.503
Well, unless you have
another $400

22:10.570 --> 22:13.370
